name: createProjectWithRunsAndSetStatus
description: Check that the test completes all necessary steps to set statuses for created test cases.
descriptionHtml: Check that the test completes all necessary steps to set statuses for created test cases.

testStage.description: Check that the test completes all necessary steps to set statuses for created test cases.

steps.name: Log in with credentials: email 'sabuk.zhenya@gmail.com' and password '!PerfectTechMeSkills6210485%'.
Creating a Project and open it.
Click on the 'Add Project' button and redirect to the 'Add Project' page.
Click on the 'Add Project' button on the 'Add Project' page.
Opening the 'Milestone' page for the project.
Click on the 'Add Milestone' button on the 'Add Milestone' page.
Opening the 'Test Cases' page for the project.
Click on the 'Add Test Case' button.
Click on the 'Save' button on the 'Add Test Case' page.
Opening the 'Test Cases' page for the project.
Click on the 'Add Test Case' button.
Click on the 'Save' button on the 'Add Test Case' page.
Opening the 'Test Cases' page for the project.
Click on the 'Add Test Case' button.
Click on the 'Save' button on the 'Add Test Case' page.
Creating a Test Run with selected Test Cases.
Opening the 'Test Runs & Results' page for the project.
Click on the 'Add Test Run' button.
Creating an Test Run with Cases.
Click on the 'Change Selection' button on the 'Add Test Run
Click on the 'Select All' button on the 'Select Cases' window.
Click on the 'Ok' button on the 'Select Cases' window.
Click on the 'Add Test Run' button on the 'Add Test Run & Results' page
Add the same status for all cases.
Click on the 'Add Results' button and window 'Add Result' is opened.
Click on the 'Add Result' button for the window 'Add Result'.
Get the value from the chart legend.
Get the value from the chart legend.
